The paper deals with generating realistic human head images using convolutional neural networks, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses meta-learning and adversarial training, which are common topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also mentions the use of portrait paintings, which could potentially fall under the graphics (cs.GR) or multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
